      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a purist\u2019s spec, featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 and a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox. The engine utilizes individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response, pulling hard to its 8,400 RPM redline. Maintenance is up to date with critical rod bearing and throttle actuator services already performed. The chassis retains its composure via Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a factory M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal power delivery through the corners. Finished with a weight-saving carbon fiber roof, this is a mechanically sound, driver-focused machine ready for the track or the open road.",
