    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Up for sale is a stunning 2018 executive sedan that perfectly blends sophisticated styling with spirited performance. The exterior is finished in a deep metallic charcoal that retains a brilliant luster, showing only the lightest evidence of careful road use. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort, featuring premium heated leather seats with minimal bolster wear, a crystal-clear premium audio system, and a responsive touchscreen interface. As a detail-oriented owner, I have ensured this vehicle never missed a scheduled service; the engine runs whisper-quiet, and the transmission shifts with seamless precision. Recent maintenance includes a fresh synthetic oil change, a new cabin air filter, and a set of high-performance all-season tires with less than 1,000 miles on them. This car has been garage-kept, smoke-free, and primarily used for highway commuting. It comes complete with a full service history, two sets of key fobs, and original floor mats. If you are looking for a reliable, turn-key luxury vehicle that looks and drives beautifully, this is the one.",
